Docker draw backs
================
	Ø DOCKER ONLY CREATES CONTIANERS NOT MANAGING 
	Ø Containers are very light weight 
	Ø Docker will not support self-healing or auto-healing
	Ø Docker will not handle LB
Docker will not support AS